title: European Street
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, International, Raw, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan raw items, made-in-house by sister company Shakti Life Kitchen, are cashew cheeze & crackers, rueben, athena's gift, sunshine sandwich, new day salad, and two desserts available daily. Serves a large amount of non-raw vegan dishes including tempeh sandwiches and hot dogs with kraut. Four different locations in Jacksonville (see website). Serves over 200 beers.
